OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh has
OL,7,Fannounced a number of measures to get
OL,8,FHS2 plans back on track due to
OL,9,F"spiralling costs".
OL,11,FMs Haigh said her immediate priority
OL,12,Fwas delivering the high speed link
OL,13,Fbetween London and Birmingham at the
OL,14,Flowest, most reasonable cost.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
