OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,FOver the years, the cost of Phase One
OL,7,Fhas soared, due to what the new
OL,8,Fgovernment has described as " poor
OL,9,Fproject management, inflation and poor
OL,10,Fperformance from the supply chain,
OL,11,Fwithout sufficient explanation of what
OL,12,Fis to be done to deliver to budget."
OL,14,FIn response, the Secretary of State
OL,15,Fhas launched an independent review to
OL,16,Fensure lessons are learned to support
OL,17,Faction and to ensure that the costs
OL,18,Ffor HS2 are brought under control.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
