OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,FThe Government has been clear it is
OL,7,Fnot resurrecting Phase 2 of HS2, which
OL,8,Fwas cancelled under the previous
OL,9,Fadministration. The Government said it
OL,10,Frecognised concerns about connectivity
OL,11,Fbetween Birmingham and Manchester but
OL,12,Fits primary focus now was the safe
OL,13,Fdelivery of HS2 between Birmingham and
OL,14,FLondon at the lowest reasonable cost,
OL,15,Fand the Secretary of State has made
OL,16,Fthis objective clear to HS2 Ltd.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
