OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast under fire: HS2
OL,7,FCutbacks threaten Manchester services
OL,9,FThe route was originally scheduled to
OL,10,Fconnect London, Birmingham, Manchester
OL,11,Fand Leeds, but was scaled back by the
OL,12,Fprevious Conservative government who
OL,13,Fscrapped 'Phase 2'.
OL,15,F'Phase 2a' was to connect the West
OL,16,FMidlands to Crewe, whilst 'Phase 2b'
OL,17,Fwas from Crewe to Manchester.
OL,19,FThe government has insisted it has no
OL,20,Fplans to resurrect Phase 2 of HS2.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
