OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,FAddressing the review, Ms Haigh said:
OL,7,F"One of my first jobs as Transport
OL,8,FSecretary has been to urgently review
OL,9,Fthe position I have inherited on HS2.
OL,11,F"It has long been clear that the costs
OL,12,Fof HS2 have been allowed to spiral out
OL,13,Fof control, but since becoming
OL,14,FTransport Secretary I have seen up
OL,15,Fclose the scale of failure in project
OL,16,Fdelivery ` and it's dire.
OL,18,F"Taxpayers have a right to expect HS2
OL,19,Fis delivered efficiently and I won't
OL,20,Fstand for anything less.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
