OL,3,CHS2 independent review launched in bid
OL,4,Cto get 'spiralling costs' back on track
OL,6,F"I have promised to work fast and fix
OL,7,Fthings and that's exactly why I have
OL,8,Fannounced urgent measures to get a
OL,9,Fgrip on HS2's costs and ensure
OL,10,Ftaxpayers' money is put to good use.
OL,12,F"It's high time we make sure lessons
OL,13,Fare learnt and the mistakes of HS2 are
OL,14,Fnever repeated again."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
